      "text": [
        "1273 - وَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «اَلْمُتَمِّمُ فِي اَلسَّفَرِ كَالْمُقَصِّرِ فِي اَلْحَضَرِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1273 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"One who prays in full (without shortening) while traveling is like the one who shortens (prayer) while residing (at home).\""
        ]
      }
    }
  },
